Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Tournament mode step 3a: Dock Mode host/join/team flows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- src/components/Tournament.jsx: new screen. Three states driven by
  data.activeTournament: (not in one) host or join-by-code + 'your tournaments'
  list; (teamless) pick or create a team; (on a team) leaderboard placeholder
  for 3b + Leave. datetime-local pickers converted to real ISO instants so the
  in-window scoring check is timezone-correct.
- src/lib/tournament.js: host/join/team ops (hostTournament, joinByCode,
  listTeams, createTeam, pickTeam, leaveTournament, myTournaments). getSession()
  for auth (local read). Unique join code from an unambiguous alphabet.
- src/App.jsx: 'tournament' nav entry (🎣) + screen render.
- src/components/LogCatch.jsx: 'Enter in tournament' opt-out toggle in the
  details step (shown only when a tournament is active), carried to the catch as
  tournOptOut. Placed inside the existing step, not a new card.
- src/styles/app.css: .tourn-toggle.

Sets data.activeTournament, which the step-2 publish path consumes.
